      "Devices are equipment with lifecycles: installation tested, batteries and connectivity on maintenance schedules (the dead pendant worn faithfully for a fortnight is the sector's recurring tragedy — battery checks are rostered, not remembered), faults escalated same-day with interim cover arranged (the human checks that resume until the sensor returns), and saf-035's machinery applied where devices are medical devices",
